uthors are redefined and many misprints corrected. Finally, the text of the Byzantine epitome of the Commentary is here edited for the first time.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn Greek, Ancient (to 1453).0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 0aMusic theoryvEarly works to 1800. 0aMusic theoryxEarly works to 1800. 0aMusic, Greek and RomanxEarly works to 1800xHistory and criticismxCriticism, interpretation, etcxEarly works. 0aMusic, Greek and RomanxHistory and criticismvEarly works to 1800. 4aHarmonik. 4aNeuplatonismus. 4aPorphyrios. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / Ancient & Classical.2bisacsh  aHarmonics.  aNeoplatonism.  aPorphyry.1 aRaffa, Massimo, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2017 Part 1z978311076249508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2017z978311071954308iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2016z9783110485103oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Classical Studies 2016z9783110485097oZDB-23-DGD0 cprintz978311042516140uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311041967240uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110419672423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110419672/original  a978-3-11-071954-3  DG Plus eBook-Package 2017b2017  a978-3-11-076249-5  DG Plus DeG Package 2017 Part 1b2017  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_CL  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGDb2016  aZDB-23-DGGb2016